    About the Product
    Description
    Nutritional Information

    Unleash the unseen with the all-new MuscleBlaze Biozyme Clear Whey Isolate, in Icy Orange flavor. This revolutionary protein supplement breaks the monotony by offering a refreshing, clear, and fruity alternative to regular milky whey protein.
    MuscleBlaze Biozyme Clear Whey Isolate is made with premium isolate protein, and powered by the patented Enhanced Absorption Formula (EAF) technology that boosts protein absorption by 50% and BCAA absorption by a whopping 60%.
    It delivers 20g of protein in just 92 calories per scoop, all while having ZERO added sugar. With no emulsifiers or thickeners added to the formula, this is perfect for those who are looking for lighter ways to refresh things up!

    A Revolution in Each Sip: MuscleBlaze Biozyme Clear Whey Isolate is a revolutionary protein supplement offering a refreshing, clear, and fruity alternative to regular milky whey protein, perfect for those looking for a convenient way to complete their protein intake.
    Premium Protein & Enhanced Absorption: Formulated with patented Biozyme EAF technology, this delivers 20g of protein per scoop, with clinically proven 50% higher absorption and 60% higher BCAA absorption for maximized results.
    Faster Recovery with 100% Whey Isolate: Ideal for those who find regular whey protein-heavy, Biozyme Clear Whey Isolate offers a lighter option, with each scoop offering 20g of protein in just 92 calories, thus promoting faster muscle recovery after workouts.

    Your Whey, Your Rules: Escape the scrutiny of summer with the burst of refreshing Icy Orange flavor. Enjoy a protein supplement that tastes as good as it is for you. And the best part? You can make a regular drink, a fruity mocktail, or even ice pops with this!
    Light on Your Stomach: The clear, easy-to-digest formula provides 20g of protein per scoop, and helps minimize digestive discomfort and bloating.

    Juice or protein? Its both!: This refreshing, zero-added sugar formula is gentle on the stomach. The Icy Orange flavor will make your taste buds wonder if this is juice or a regular protein shake. It wont even froth up, like what happens with generic clear whey protein.
    Zero-Added Sugar: Unlike sugary protein drinks, Biozyme Clear Whey Isolate keeps your sugar intake in check while providing the protein your muscles crave.
    Consumption Direction:
    Add one 27g level scoop in 300-400ml water, and shake vigorously for about 15-30 seconds for uniform mixing. Unlike other Clear Whey Protein that froths up, MuscleBlaze Biozyme Clear Whey Isolate settles in just 30 to 60 seconds, ensuring a smooth drinking experience.
